<main id="content" class="content"> <h1 class="title">No True Patriot
 <br></br> <span class="subtitle">Apr 04, 2025 17:00</span>
</h1>
 <blockquote class="bigquote">
 <p>
’My country, right or wrong,’ is a thing that no true patriot would think of saying. . . . It is like saying, ’My
mother, drunk or sober’.
</p>
</blockquote>

 <p class="bigquote">
G. K. Chesterton
</p>

